                    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/smallsmile/">smallsmile</a>
                        <span class="user-stars allstar40 rating" title="推荐"></span>
                    <span>2007-05-02</span>
                </span>
            </h3>
            <p class="comment-content">关注这种学术著作的人毕竟是少数</p>
        </div>
    </li>

                
    <li class="comment-item" data-cid="513944000">
        <div class="comment">
            <h3>
